SQL_STMT_U.val: select cast(sum(ACCC_MUTAFACTORING) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(ACCC_MUTASPECIAL ) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(ACCC_MUTAINVESTMENT ) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(ACCC_MUTARETENTION) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(ACCC_MUTADISPUTES) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(ACCC_MUTAEXTRAFIN) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/ACCC where ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO = :2 and ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO = :3 and ACCC_ACCT_DATE = ':4' and ACCC_MUTTYPE >= 95 for fetch only optimize for 100 rows

select CLNT108_ACC_CURR, cast(sum(ACCC_MUTAFACTORING) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(ACCC_MUTASPECIAL ) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(ACCC_MUTAINVESTMENT ) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(ACCC_MUTARETENTION ) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(ACCC_MUTADISPUTES ) as decimal (13,2)), cast(sum(ACCC_MUTAEXTRAFIN) as decimal (13,2)) from :1/ACCC, :1/CLNT where ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO = CLNT101_ADMNO and CLNT:2_ADMNO = :3 and ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO = CLNT102_CLNTNO and CLNT:4_CLNTNO = :5 and ACCC_ACCT_DATE = ':6' and ACCC_MUTTYPE >= 95 group by CLNT108_ACC_CURR for fetch only optimize for 100 rows
